                19,803 次收藏</div></div></div></div><div class="Card FollowshipCard"><div class="NumberBoard FollowshipCard-counts NumberBoard--divider"><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/org/xin-fa-xian-93/following"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注了</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="2">2</strong></div></a><a type="button" class="Button NumberBoard-item Button--plain" href="/org/xin-fa-xian-93/followers"><div class="NumberBoard-itemInner"><div class="NumberBoard-itemName">关注者</div><strong class="NumberBoard-itemValue" title="19121">19,121</strong></div></a></div></div><div class="Card"><a class="Profile-createOrgAccount" target="_blank" href="https://www.zhihu.com/org/signup">开通机构号</a></div><div class="Profile-lightList"><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/xin-fa-xian-93/following/topics"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的话题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">10</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/xin-fa-xian-93/following/columns"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的专栏</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">0</span></a><a class="Profile-lightItem" href="/org/xin-fa-xian-93/following/questions"><span class="Profile-lightItemName">关注的问题</span><span class="Profile-lightItemValue">31</span></a></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><div id="data" style="display:none" data-state="{&quot;common&quot;:{&quot;ask&quot;:{}},&quot;privacy&quot;:{&quot;showPrivacy&quot;:false},&quot;loading&quot;:{&quot;global&quot;:{&quot;count&quot;:0},&quot;local&quot;:{&quot;people/get/&quot;:false,&quot;people/getActivities/xin-fa-xian-93&quot;:false}},&quot;entities&quot;:{&quot;users&quot;:{&quot;xin-fa-xian-93&quot;:{&quot;isFollowed&quot;:false,&quot;educations&quot;:[],&quot;followingCount&quot;:2,&quot;voteFromCount&quot;:0,&quot;locations&quot;:[],&quot;includedText&quot;:&quot;知乎圆桌和编辑推荐&quot;,&quot;pinsCount&quot;:20,&quot;isFollowing&quot;:false,&quot